{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/VariedGameplayGif_v4.gif?t=1737986972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ARM OF SATAN is a tough precision platformer designed for <i>2-player co-op</i>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring <strong>kick ass visuals</strong> influenced by the <i>Hellboy</i> comics, <strong>arcade-inspired</strong> gameplay, and a <strong>deep</strong> and <strong>captivating narrative</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game can be played single-player as a <i>difficult twin-stick</i>, but it is designed to be a <i>truly awesome</i> <strong>co-op experience</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/MeetTheHeroes.gif?t=1737986972\" />Arm of Satan follows the journey of two characters: <strong>Girl &amp; Arm</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Girl </strong>should not be here. <strong>Arm</strong> claims to know a way out\u2026 Together, they descend through the underworlds in search of <i>salvation</i>\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GIRL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/PlayAsGirl.gif?t=1737986972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Girl controls like a classic platformer. She is in charge of movement and jumping.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(great for onboarding newer or younger players).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ARM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/PlayAsArm.gif?t=1737986972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arm is an action-oriented reflex machine: grabbing, punching and throwing everything and anything to protect Girl.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TOGETHER...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/Girl_ArmCombined.gif?t=1737986972\" /><strong>Girl &amp; Arm must synchronise to platform, traverse, dodge and climb their way through the treacherous depths of the underworlds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the many underworlds, inspired by diverse cultural depictions of the afterlife.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/MeetTheDenizens.png?t=1737986972\" /><strong>Engage (at your own risk) with the many denizens of the underworlds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/ArcadeMode_Tribs.gif?t=1737986972\" /><strong>Finished the story? Play endlessly in ARCADE MODE, the dedicated speedrunning mode with tonnes of 'Tribulations' that challenge you to set fast times.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/extras/LOGOIncubator_Ludophoria_ArmOfSatan.png?t=1737986972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your eyes on our community discord for news, insights and details.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737986972","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388750/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737986972","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic